Package: BayesEFA
Title: Bayesian Exploratory Factor Analysis Using Stan
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Rey-Sáez", , "ricardoreysaez95@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6739-2035"))
Description: Implements Bayesian Exploratory Factor Analysis (EFA) with efficient sampling via 'Stan'. Supports dedicated factors, various rotation methods (including rotational indeterminacy correction using the RSP algorithm), and custom prior specifications. Provides tools for factor structure visualization, model fit assessment, and reliability analysis.
